text: @UPSHelp How am I meant to reschedule a delivery if I work full time before 5pm and when I ring there is an automated line that goes in circles and the website will now not let me log in to track... worst birthday present delivery ever!

@emma_woolner I can certainly see how this would be frustrating to not get your package because you are working. If you need us to look into this please DM us your tracking number, complete address, and phone number. ^AC
